{"tid":1472123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"提款作家用","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T02:45:10.000Z","uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0676741924128e162a3b2ebf348568b1e1bd08a8","tid":1472123,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:00:54.000Z","msg":"相信好多人都對提款抗暴政有所遲疑，<br />\n<br />\n我比個理由你吧！<br />\n<br />\n你可以提一年家用的數量，<br />\n<br />\n家中有安全地方就每月比月費，<br />\n<br />\n變相不用每月排隊提款，方便又實用。<br />\n<br />\n或者一炮過給一年家用。<br />\n<br />\n到現時這階段，讓我們提家用救香港！<br />\n<br />\n提家用，做孝子！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eee7f19b5d97595f192e76e1eb9cb692137ecc1","tid":1472123,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"提家用，做孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a6eb194712f406abf8b1061922b076b4fd0a51","tid":1472123,"uid":270863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"bfe26115f24ccab9cbdf9b922378db90d63cdf13","tid":1472123,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"每日做孝子 日日去提款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}